g.ns11:text: \\begin{flalign*}\n& \\phi_1 = \\int_{0}^{t} V I d t \\:, &\\\\\n& \\phi_2 = \\int_{0}^{t} I^{2} d t \\:, &\n\\end{flalign*}
$V = \\left( E_0 + E_1 (\\phi_1+R \\phi_2) + \\left(E_{2,0}+E_{2,1} I+E_{2,2} I^{2}\\right) \\exp \\left[\\left(E_{3,0}+E_{3,1} I\\right) (\\phi_1+R \\phi_2) \\right]\\right) + R I$

\begin{flalign*}
 \nonumber
 & V = \left[ E_0^d + \left( E_{1,0}^d + E_{1,1}^d I + E_{1,2}^d I^2 \right)(\phi_1+R \phi_2) + \left(E_{2,0}^{d} + E_{2,1}^{d} I + E_{2,2}^{d} I^{2}\right)\exp \left((E_{3,0}^d + E_{3,1}^d)(\phi_1 \right. \right. &\\
 \nonumber
 & \phantom{abcde} + \left. \left. R \phi_2) + E_{4,1}^d \exp \left( E_{4,2}^d(\phi_1 + R \phi_2) \right) \right) \right] + (R_{d,0} + R_{d,1}I) I &\\
 & \phantom{abcde} +\left(E_{5,1}^{d} - E_{5,2}^{d} (\phi_1 + R \phi_2) \right) \cos \left((\phi_1 + R \phi_2) E_{5,3}^{d} \right)\:.&
\end{flalign*}

\begin{flalign*}
 \nonumber
 & V = \left[ E_0^d + \left( E_{1,0}^d + E_{1,1}^d I + E_{1,2}^d I^2 \right)(\phi_1+R \phi_2) + \left(E_{2,0}^{d} + E_{2,1}^{d} I + E_{2,2}^{d} I^{2}\right)\exp \left((E_{3,0}^d + E_{3,1}^d)(\phi_1 \right. \right. &\\
 \nonumber
 & \phantom{abcde} + \left. \left. R \phi_2) + E_{4,1}^d \exp \left( E_{4,2}^d(\phi_1 + R \phi_2) \right) \right) \right] + (R_{d,0} + R_{d,1}I) I &\\
 \nonumber
 & \phantom{abcde} + \left(E_{5,1}^{d} - E_{5,2}^{d} (\phi_1 + R \phi_2) \right) \cos \left((\phi_1 + R \phi_2) E_{5,3}^{d} \right)&\\
 \nonumber
 & \phantom{abcde} +(E_{6,1}^{d}) \cos \left((\phi_1 + R \phi_2) E_{6,2}^{d} \right) &\\
 &\phantom{abcde} +(E_{7,1}^{d}) \cos \left((\phi_1 + R \phi_2) E_{7,2}^{d} \right) \:.&
\end{flalign*}
